HEADWORD: Judas-colored
<hw>Ju"das-col`ored</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Red; -- from a
tradition that <person>Judas Iscariot</person> had red hair and
beard.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>There's treachery in that <qex>Judas-colored</qex> beard.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Juddock</ent>⟦br⟧
